## TITLE('Biochemistry: Classify a reaction by EC enzyme class')
## DESCRIPTION
## Given a biochemical reaction shown with RDKit.js molecular structures and cofactor text, select the correct EC enzyme class from six choices. Covers all six EC classes (oxidoreductases, transferases, hydrolases, lyases, isomerases, ligases) with 24 reactions drawn from central metabolism.
## ENDDESCRIPTION
## KEYWORDS('enzyme classification','EC number','which one')
## DBsubject('Biochemistry')
## DBchapter('Enzymes')
## DBsection('Enzyme Classification')
## Level(2)
## Date('2026-02-26')
## Author('Dr. Neil R. Voss')
## Institution('Roosevelt University')
## Language(en)
